  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThe following code causes OOM: \r\n```java\r\n  private final SnappyBlockCompressor compressor = new SnappyBlockCompressor();\r\n\r\n  @Test\r\n  public void uncompress_hugeFakePayload() {\r\n    Bytes hugeLength = ProtobufEncoder.encodeVarInt(Integer.MAX_VALUE);\r\n    final Bytes data =\r\n        Bytes.concatenate(\r\n            hugeLength, Bytes.fromHexString(\"000000000000000000000000\"));\r\n\r\n    assertThatThrownBy(() -> compressor.uncompress(data)).isInstanceOf(DecodingException.class);\r\n  }\r\n```\r\n\r\nThanks @tintinweb for this finding: https://github.com/ethereum/public-attacknets/issues/15",
